summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6066 for the construction of a trunk sewer together with a storm water overflow known as THE WEST MONTLAKE TRUNK SEWER UNIT NO. 2; under Ordinance No. 83003 (as amended by Ordinance No. 83410), and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
